title: Hugo Boss perfume
Specifics of the nature of the perfume to be mentioned.
review:
I'm a huge fan of Hugo Boss perfumes. Actually I love this perfume, but it
looks to me this one is little diluted compared to the one I used in Germany.
I don't know this smells exactly the same but not lasting for a while.

It's really great that proper information and guidance for selection of
perfumes is mentioned in the product details. If you could add the fragrance
description it would be really helpful.  
I've given a four ⭐️ as I have used this unable to decide which one to choose
as the fragrance is not mentioned. I prefer woody (cedar) and musk which suit
my body type.
